o is now reversed. Less than 1 in 5 adults has not received any formal educ=
ation.
This is reflected in literacy data [ https://substack.com/redirect/6c0e8cb2=
-70e4-48fd-9361-fd5baa987f76?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXX=
epKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ], too: 200 years ago, very few could read and write. =
